{"title":"山海情——林业疗养区诗笺","authors":["吴宝三"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":12,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山海情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——林业疗养区诗笺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴宝三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首山吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪是众山首？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人称倍愧羞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未曾做过飞天的好梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是一座普通的山丘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不似泰山雄伟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却有骨骼肌肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀抱花草，守护种籽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松涛里是生命交响曲的伴奏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不似黄山瑰丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亦有彩云行走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观日出日落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白帆飘进海市蜃楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心和大地相连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月把性格铸就；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待到大海呼唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化一只鼓浪的海鸥……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，海滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海浪寻觅知音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温泉汩汩弹琴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿树举起春天的旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎劳动者莅临！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小溪向大海汇积，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山岫吸引白云——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工、海员、勘探者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶着勒勒车的草原牧民……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走了的，留下盛开心花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了的，洗去满身征尘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然坐落在山海关外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却终年是春……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伐木者的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除祛痼疾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对大海不胜感激；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掬朵朵温泉浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向大地深致谢意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似江河向往大海哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种籽渴望土地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似喷涌的温泉哟——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热力在高山下积聚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕子的双翅带来春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天上小鸟衔来春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳拥抱的屋顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴嗒，飞下一串儿水滴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按捺不住似箭的归心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在屋檐下让水珠淋漓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，干旱的心田润湿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中的青山长绿……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}